title: 097: Brandan Schieppati- Rise Above Fitness & Bleeding Through Lead Singer
description: Sal, Adam & Justin interview Brandan Schieppati, the owner of the Rise Above Fitness Gym & Apparel brand and the lead singer of Bleeding Through. Brandan also happens to have a podcast right here on iTunes (search Brandan Schieppati's Podcast) and shares many of the opinions held by the MindPump Crew. WARNING!: This episode is not safe for fitness posers and charlatans! You can also find Brandan on Instagram @brandanschieppati
